ActFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
Canada Transportation Act
SubjectSettlement Agreement Disposition of federal real property Acquisition of real property Oshawa Harbour
PrecisOrder approving the Settlement Agreement to settle long-standing land-related issues and disputes between the City of Oshawa on one hand and the Crown (Transport Canada) and the Oshawa Harbour Commission (OHC), including all issues raised in a lawsuit brought by the City of Oshawa against the Crown, the OHC and Canadian National Railway (CNR).
